t: Amazon.co.uk: Gateway
Amazon API Gateway Pricing | API Management | Amazon Web Services
s: With Amazon API Gateway, you only pay when your APIs are in use. There are no minimum fees or upfront commitments. For HTTP APIs and REST APIs, you pay only for the API calls you receive and the amount of data transferred out. There are no data transfer out charges for Private APIs.
